      "Adjustable Coverage with a Natural Appearance: This BB cream offers flexible coverage that helps improve the look of pores, blemishes, and uneven tone. The texture feels light and breathable on the skin, blending into a soft, naturally radiant finish that remains comfortable during daily wear without a heavy or greasy appearance",
