      "Smooth Application with Balanced Wear Performance: The cushion-style design uses a flexible film structure to dispense a controlled amount of product for even application. It helps enhance overall brightness and soften the appearance of imperfections while maintaining a lightweight, breathable feel during use",
      "Light Moisture with a Skin-Like Finish: Featuring a water-based texture, this formula delivers light moisture without weighing the skin down. The finish leans toward a fresh, dewy look that supports a natural, skin-like appearance and ongoing comfort throughout the day",
      "Easy Application for a Refined Look: Apply after completing your regular skincare steps. Use the included cushion puff to gently press and pat the product onto the skin, helping achieve a smooth and blended result. A setting spray may be used to enhance makeup stability and maintain a natural-looking finish"
